OL,3,CFury as airport conference centre
OL,4,Cplans recommended for refusal
OL,6,FThe head of Jersey's Chamber of
OL,7,FCommerce says he is "aghast" at the
OL,8,F"frankly ridiculous" recommendation by
OL,9,Fa planning officer to refuse proposals
OL,10,Ffor a major conference centre opposite
OL,11,Fthe island's airport.
OL,13,FDesigns for a six-storey complex in St
OL,14,FPeter - including a luxury hotel with
OL,15,Fup to 179 rooms, a restaurant,
OL,16,Fswimming pool and spa - were submitted
OL,17,Fback in August.
