OL,3,CFury as airport conference centre
OL,4,Cplans recommended for refusal
OL,6,FJersey's Island Bridging Plan states
OL,7,Fthat developments of eight storeys or
OL,8,Funder can be supported outside of town
OL,9,Fif they meet various conditions,
OL,10,Fincluding being "appropriate to the
OL,11,Ftownscape character of the area".
OL,13,FIn recommending refusal, the planning
OL,14,Fofficer states that while "there are
OL,15,Fclear economic benefits" to the
OL,16,Fproject and a large number of
OL,17,Fsupportive submissions, it would be
OL,18,F"overly dominant" and harm the
OL,19,Flandscape.
