OL,3,CFury as airport conference centre
OL,4,Cplans recommended for refusal
OL,6,FConcerns are also raised over the
OL,7,Fbenefit members of the public would
OL,8,Fget from the leisure facilities, as
OL,9,Fwell as increased road traffic, flood
OL,10,Frisk, the impact on protected species,
OL,11,Fand that the site's residential
OL,12,Faccommodation would fail housing
OL,13,Fquality standards.
OL,15,FIt would be the tallest building
OL,16,Foutside of St Helier and public
OL,17,Fcomments highlight worries over the
OL,18,Fdevelopment's size.
