OL,6,FHowever, the President of the island's
OL,7,FChamber of Commerce, Lee Madden, says
OL,8,Fthe plans must be allowed to go ahead
OL,9,Fas they offer "a transformative
OL,10,Fopportunity for Jersey's hospitality
OL,11,Fsector, creating jobs, attracting year-
OL,12,Fround tourism and supporting local
OL,13,Fsport".
