OL,3,CFury as airport conference centre
OL,4,Cplans recommended for refusal
OL,6,FHe adds: "I am aghast at the Planning
OL,7,FDepartment's recommendation to reject
OL,8,Fthe Strive hotel proposal. The
OL,9,FBridging Island Plan (BIP), in its
OL,10,Fcurrent form, is no longer fit for
OL,11,Fpurpose and must be removed as a rigid
OL,12,Fpoint of reference when assessing
OL,13,Fdevelopments that offer clear
OL,14,Feconomic, social and community
OL,15,Fbenefits.
OL,17,F"To dismiss the staff accommodation
OL,18,Fbecause it doesn't meet SPG standards
OL,19,Fis frankly ridiculous. This is staff
OL,20,Faccommodation, not permanent
OL,21,Fresidential housing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
