OL,6,F"We urge the Planning Committee to
OL,7,Flook beyond outdated constraints and
OL,8,Fembrace a vision that supports growth,
OL,9,Finnovation and the long-term
OL,10,Fprosperity of our island.
OL,12,F"With strong support from Visit
OL,13,FJersey, Jersey Sport, the Economy
OL,14,FDepartment and the Jersey Rugby Club,
OL,15,Fthis application deserves approval."
OL,17,FA final decision will be made by the
OL,18,Fisland's Planning Committee on
OL,19,FThursday 6 November.
